These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, japanese, indonesian, american
4 different pets are kept: turtle, lizard, goat, frog
1. the owner of the frog is not to the right of the owner of the turtle##8
2. the owner of the frog is on the right of the turkish##1
3. the japanese is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
4. the american is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
5. the american is not to the left of the owner of the frog##8
6. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the japanese##5
7. the japanese is somewhere between the turkish and the owner of the lizard##7
8. the japanese and the owner of the frog have the same parity positions##9
9. the indonesian and the owner of the turtle have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | turkish | japanese | indonesian     | american |
| Pet           | goat   | frog     | lizard | turtle  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, 7up, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, woodworking, collecting, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games and the person drinking lemonade have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
6. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
7. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk     | 7up    | iced-tea | lemonade    |
| Hobby      | fishing | woodworking | collecting      | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, sprite, almond-milk, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, lettuce, cucumber, grapes
1. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person eating cucumber##5
2. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
7. the person eating cranberry is not to the left of the person eating lettuce##8
8. the person drinking sprite and the person eating lettuce have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | sprite    | almond-milk   | tea    | mirinda  |
| Food       | lettuce | grapes | cranberry | cucumber |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, social-worker, teacher, bartender
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, jazz, gospel, folk
1. the fan soul is the social-worker##1
2. the fan jazz is on the right of the fan gospel##1
3. the fan jazz is somewhere to the left of the social-worker##5
4. the fan folk is on the left or right of the teacher##3
5. the fan jazz is on the left of the electrician##1
6. the bartender and the fan folk have the same parity positions##9
7. the teacher is on the left or right of the electrician##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | bartender | teacher | electrician  | social-worker |
| Music-Genre   | gospel             | jazz          | folk | soul    |

