.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, jazz, techno, pop
4 different pets are kept: lizard, rat, snake, guinea-pig
1. the fan techno is not the owner of the snake##6
2. the owner of the lizard and the fan reggae have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the rat and the fan jazz have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the fan techno##5
5. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the fan pop##1
6. the fan jazz is not the owner of the rat##6
7. the fan pop is somewhere to the left of the fan jazz##5
8. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the fan reggae##1
9. the owner of the guinea-pig is not the fan pop##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | techno | pop  | jazz |
| Pet           | rat   | lizard     | snake | guinea-pig      |

