2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
3. the polish is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
4. the spanish and the person watching horror movies have the same parity positions##9
5. the person watching epic movies and the spanish have different parity positions##9
6. the polish is not to the left of the person watching drama movies##8
7. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
8. the person watching disaster movies is not to the right of the malaysian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | drama | horror | epic |
| Nationality   | malaysian        | polish    | spanish   | canadian |

