3. the person who's sport is weightlifting and the fan reggae have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the fan reggae is not to the right of the fan disco##8
6. the fan ambient is somewhere to the left of the fan disco##5
7. the fan reggae is somewhere to the right of the fan rock##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | rock    | ambient | reggae         | disco     |
| Sport         | rowing | weightlifting  | snowboarding | basketball |

