.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, chess, hiking, drawing
4 different pets are kept: goat, hedgehog, frog, turtle
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere between the owner of the goat and the owner of the hedgehog##7
2. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the right of the owner of the turtle##8
3. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
5. the person who's hobby is chess is not the owner of the goat##6
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
7. the person who's hobby is drawing and the owner of the turtle have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | drawing | chess | traveling | hiking |
| Pet     | hedgehog     | frog     | turtle     | goat    |

