.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, grapefruit, cherry, spinach
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, subway, helicopter, roller
1. the person driving the roller is not to the left of the person eating pomegranate##8
2. the person eating spinach and the person driving the roller have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
4. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
5. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the person driving the roller##7
6. the person eating spinach is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | cherry | pomegranate   | grapefruit | spinach |
| Transport   | helicopter   | subway | van    | roller      |

