3. the person eating pear is not to the left of the person eating eggplant##8
4. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
5. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
6. the dutch is on the far left##1
7. the indonesian is on the left of the person eating pear##1
8. the person eating cherry is the brazilian##1
9. the person eating eggplant and the indonesian have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
