The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, martial-arts, lemonadesy, zombie
1. the person watching action movies is not the person drinking juice##6
2. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching lemonadesy movies##1
6. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
8. the person watching action movies and the person drinking 7up have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching lemonadesy movies and the person drinking hot-chocolate have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice   | lemonade  | hot-chocolate  | 7up |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | lemonadesy | zombie | action      |

