.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk, juice, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, trance, house, salsa
 1. the person drinking almond-milk and the fan house have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 3. the fan pop is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking cola##7
 4. the fan house is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
 5. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan house is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
 7. the person drinking iced-tea and the fan trance have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan salsa##3
 9. the fan salsa is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the fan pop##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola  | iced-tea | juice  | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | house     | pop | trance     |

