4 different pets are kept: rabbit, lizard, pony, dog
1. the musician and the owner of the rabbit have the same parity positions##9
2. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the accountant is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
4. the musician is not to the right of the project-manager##8
5. the owner of the rabbit is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the pony and the designer have the same parity positions##9
7. the owner of the rabbit and the accountant have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |     3      |       4        |
| Job   | designer | musician | project-manager | accountant |
