2. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person drinking cola and the person who's hobby is card-games have the same parity positions##9
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite    | cola | juice | tea |
| Hobby      | reading | card-games   | woodworking   | rock-climbing   |

