.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, lemonade, mirinda, iced-tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, dancing, sudoku, baking
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
 4. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is not the person drinking lemonade##6
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
 7. the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's hobby is dancing have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
10. the person drinking lemonade and the person who's hobby is dancing have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | mirinda        | iced-tea   | soy-milk      |
| Hobby      | baking | sudoku | dancing | cooking |

 